eb.archive.org/web/20140101102310/http://library.neit.edu/currevnt.htm |archivedate=2014-01-01 }}</ref> \n* [[University of Pennsylvania]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://onlinebooks.library.upenn.edu/archives.html|title=The Online Books Page: Archives and Indexes|website=onlinebooks.library.upenn.edu}}</ref> \n* [http://www.baylor.edu/church_state/ John M. Dawson Institute for Church State Studies]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.baylor.edu/church_state/index.php?id=36042|title=Links Related to the Study of Islam and Democracy|website=J.M Dawson Institute of Church-State Studies - Baylor University}}</ref> \n* [[Florida Christian College]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.fcc.edu/library/subjectguides/missions.asp |title=Archived copy |accessdate=2012-02-25 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120126152627/http://www.fcc.edu/library/subjectguides/missions.asp |archivedate=2012-01-26 }}</ref> \n* [[Westfield State University]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://lib.westfield.ma.edu/religion.htm |title=Archived copy |accessdate=2012-02-25 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130414112841/http://lib.westfield.ma.edu/religion.htm |archivedate=2013-04-14 }}</ref> \n* [[National Humanities Center]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://nationalhumanitiescenter.org/tserve/twenty/tlinksislam.htm|title=Islam in America, Essay-Related Twentieth-Century Links to Online Resources, Divining America, TeacherServe, National Humanities Center|website=nationalhumanitiescenter.org}}</ref> \n* [[University of Wisconsin\u2013Madison]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://mideast.wisc.edu/outreach/religion.htm |title=Archived copy |access-date=2012-02-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110826075046/http://mideast.wisc.edu/outreach/religion.htm |archive-date=2011-08-26 |url-status=dead }}</ref> \n* [[Northern Virginia Community College]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://novaonline.nvcc.edu/eli/evans/HIS111/Notes/Islam.html|title=Notes on early Islam|first=Charles T.|last=Evans|web