tps://books.google.com/books?id=KzeCCgAAQBAJ&pg=PA104}}\n* {{cite book|author=MacKellar, Landis|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=LJz0k9-6qlMC&pg=PA371&lpg=PA371&dq=samantha+eggar+double+indemnity&source=bl&ots=04L_mw5YPr&sig=czY-sQq7nD07_1UJ7tq8E3fGbgs&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwjhvKzoz5DKAhVFKyYKHUhTCj8Q6AEITzAK#v=onepage&q=samantha%20eggar%20double%20indemnity&f=false|year=2006|publisher=Syracuse University Press|ref={{SfnRef|MacKellar|2006}}|title=Double Indemnity Murder: Ruth Snyder, Judd Gray, and New York\u2019s Crime of the Century|isbn= 978-0-815-60824-0}}\n* {{cite book|title=Blood Money: A History of the First Teen Slasher Film Cycle|author=Nowell, Richard|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=6faoAwAAQBAJ&pg=PA281|isbn=978-1-441-12496-8|publisher=Bloomsbury Academic|ref={{SfnRef|Nowell|2010}}}}\n\n==External links==\n{{Commons category|Samantha Eggar}}\n* {{IMDb name|0002058}}\n* {{Screenonline name|id=493985|name=Samantha Eggar biography and credits}}\n* [http://www.samanthaeggar.net Official website]\n\n{{Navboxes\n|title = Awards for Samantha Eggar\n|list =\n{{Prix d'interpr\u00e9tation f\u00e9minine 1960\u20131979}}\n{{GoldenGlobeBestActressMotionPictureDrama 1961-1980}}\n}}\n\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Eggar, Samantha}}\n[[Category:1939 births]]\n[[Category:20th-century English actresses]]\n[[Category:21st-century English actresses]]\n[[Category:Actresses from London]]\n[[Category:Best Drama Actress Golden Globe (film) winners]] <!-- The Collector -->\n[[Category:Cannes Film Festival Award for Best Actress winners]]\n[[Category:British expatriate actresses in the United States]]\n[[Category:English Shakespearean actresses]]\n[[Category:English expatriates in the United States]]\n[[Category:English film actresses]]\n[[Category:English people of Dutch descent]]\n[[Category:English people of Irish descent]]\n[[Category:English people of Portuguese descent]]\n[[Category:English Roman Catholics]]\n[[Category:English soap opera actresses]]\n[[